<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        .body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .link {
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }

        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #4CAF50; /* Green */
            border: none;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #333333;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        ul li {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 5px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="body">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="header">
                <!-- Optionally include a logo here -->
                <!-- <img src="your-logo-url.png" alt="Your Company Logo"> -->
                <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Hello <%= customerName %>,</p>

                <p>Thank you for signing up with <%= companyName %>! To complete your registration, please verify your
                    email address by clicking the button below:</p>

                <a href="<%= verificationLink %>" class="button">Verify Your Email</a>

                <p>If the button above does not work, please copy and paste the following link into your browser's
                    address bar:</p>

                <p class="link"><a href="<%= verificationLink %>"><%= verificationLink %></a></p>
                
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> This link is valid for three days.</p>

                <h3>Why verify your email?</h3>

                <ul>
                    <li>To ensure the security of your account.</li>
                    <li>To receive important updates and notifications.</li>
                    <li>To complete your registration process.</li>
                </ul>

                <p>If you did not create an account with us, please ignore this email.</p>

                <p>For any questions or assistance, feel free to contact our support team at <%= supportEmail %> or <%= supportPhoneNumber %>.</p>

                <p>Best regards,</p>
                <p><%= companyName %></p>
                <p><a href="<%= companyWebsiteUrl %>"><%= companyWebsiteUrl %></a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p><%= companyWebsiteUrl %></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
